channel.title: PsyKe Out
channel.description: Podcast for the Psy-Trance (Psychedelic Trance) Radio Show, PsyKe Out. Official Website - http://www.PsyKeOut.net

image.title: PsyKe Out Podcast!
image.description: Podcast for the popular PsyTrance (Psychedelic Trance) Radio Show, PsyKe Out. Featuring various guest Psy-Trance DJs, Artists, and Labels.

item.title: PsyKe Out: March 2009 Mix - Nabi Records: International PsyTrance Association
item.description: Recording from PsyKe Out from March 2009. After a long break we have a new mix set to share with you. A promo mix of the currently unavailable compilation from Nabi Records, International PsyTrance Association. For more details about Nabi Records go to www.nabi-records.com

item.title: PsyKe Out: March 2007 Mix - Rapid Psykedelic Sonances Mix Set
item.description: Recording from PsyKe Out DJ Cyberwlf. Recorded in March 2007 just before departing from Australia for Japan, UK, and Europe.

item.title: PsyKe Out: February 2007 Show - Parvati Records: PsyStories III
item.description: Recording of PsyKe Out - the PsyTrance radio show, from February 2007. Showcasing the latest compilation from Parvati Records with the compilation PsyStories III. For more details about Parvati Records go to www.parvati-records.com

item.title: PsyKe Out Special Edition: 5th December 2006 Show - D-A-R-K Records: Dark Summer, Crazy Ducks, Faxi Nadu EPs
item.description: Recording of PsyKe Out - the PsyTrance radio show, from the 5th December 2006. Showcasing three new EPs from DARK Records from the artists Dark Summer, Crazy Ducks, Faxi Nadu. For more details about D-A-R-K Records go to www.dark-records.com

item.title: PsyKe Out Special Edition: 24th October 2006 Show - Nabi Records: 'PsyTrance is Dead!'

item.description: Recording of PsyKe Out - the PsyTrance radio show, from the 31st October 2006. Showcasing two Manic Dragon Records releases - their latest compilation Multiple Personalities 2, as well as the solo self-titled album by Baphomet Engine. For more details about Manic Dragon Records go to www.sonic-dragon.com
